Name:           perl-CGI-Application-Plugin-TT
Version:        1.05
Release:        8%{?dist}
Summary:        Add Template Toolkit support to CGI::Application
License:        GPL+ or Artistic
Group:          Development/Libraries
URL:            http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Application-Plugin-TT/
